t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https://www.mizuho.co.jp/recruit/environment/\">働く環境</a></li>\n \t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https://www.mizuho.co.jp/recruit/infographics/\">数字で見るミズホ</a></li>\n \t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https://www.mizuho.co.jp/recruit/systems/\">各種制度</a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https://www.mizuho.co.jp/media/\" onclick=\"gtag('event', 'click', {'event_category': 'click_to_media_header','event_label': 'click_to_media_header'});\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">メディア協力</a></li>\n \t\t\t\t\t\t</ul>\n \t\t\t\t\t</li>\n \t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"navlist dropdown\">\n \t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://www.mizuho.co.jp/recruit/interview/\" class=' link-gnav'>\n \t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"en\">INTERVIEW</span>\n \t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"ja\">先輩インタビュー</span>\n \t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n \t\t\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"dropdown-menu\">\n \t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https://www.mizuho.co.jp/recruit/interview/itakura/\">営業職 入社7年目</a></li>\n \t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https://www.mizuho.co.jp/recruit/interview/ura/\">営業職 入社3年目</a></li>\n \t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https://www.mizuho.co.jp/recruit/interview/tsuchiya/\">技術職 入社8年目</a></li>\n \t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https://www.mizuho.co.jp/recruit/interview/nakamura/\">品質管理 入社10年目</a></li>\n \t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https://www.mizuho.co.jp/recruit/interview/sato/\">製造部 入社19年目</a></li>\n \t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https://www.mizuho.co.jp/recruit/interview/kotani/\">海外業務 入社9年目</a></li>\n \t\t\t\t\t\t</ul>\n \t\t\t\t\t</li>\n \t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"navlist dropdown\">\n \t\t\t\t\t\t<span class='link-gnav '>\n \t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"en\">REQUIREMENTS</span>\n \t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"ja\">募集要項</span>\n \t\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n \t\t\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"dropdown-menu\">\n \t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https://www.mizuho.co.jp/recruit/requirements-01/\">新卒募集要項</a></li>\n \t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https://www.mizuho.co.jp/recruit/requirements-02/\">中途募集要項</a></li>\n \t\t\t\t\t\t</ul>\n \t\t\t\t\t</li>\n \t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"navlist\">\n \t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://www.mizuho.co.jp/recruit/faq/\" class=' link-gnav'>\n \t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"en\">FAQ</span>\n \t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"ja\">よくある質問</span>\n \t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n \t\t\t\t\t</li>\n \t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"navlist\">\n            <a href=\"https://job.mynavi.jp/27/pc/search/corp227148/outline.html\" class=\"img-btn link-gnav mynavi\" target=\"_blank\">\n              <img src=\"https://job.mynavi.jp/conts/kigyo/2027/logo/banner_logo_195_60.gif\" alt=\"マイナビ2027\" border=\"0\" style=\"max-width: 190px;\">\n            </a>\n \t\t\t\t\t</li>\n \t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"navlist\">\n \t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://www.mizuho.co.jp/recruit/entry/\" class='entry link-gnav'>\n \t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"en\">ENTRY</span>\n \t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"ja\">エントリー</span>\n \t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n \t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n \t\t\t\t</ul>\n \t\t\t</nav>\n \t\t</div>\n \t</div>\n\n </header>\n\n\n <main role=\"main\" class=\"main \">\n<div class=\"pgttl\">\n\t<div class=\"inner-pgttl\">\n\t\t<div class=\"txt\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"wrapper-en\"><p class=\"en\">Environment</p></div>\n\t\t\t<div><h1 class=\"ja\">働く環境</h1></div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"bg photo-ofi\">\n\t\t\t<img src=\"https://www.mizuho.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/mizuho1.2.7/img/common/bg-pgttl-environment.jpg\" alt=\"働く環境\">\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"breadcrumbs\">\n\t<ul class=\"list-inline\" itemscope itemtype=\"http://schema.org/BreadcrumbList\"><li itemprop=\"itemListElement\" itemscope itemtype=\"http://schema.org/ListItem\"><a href=\"https://www.mizuho.co.jp/recruit/\" class=\"home\" itemprop=\"item\" ><span itemprop=\"name\">TOP</span></a><meta itemprop=\"position\" content=\"1\" /></li><li itemprop=\"itemListElement\" itemscope itemtype=\"http://schema.org/ListItem\"><span itemprop=\"name\">働く環境</span><meta itemprop=\"position\" content=\"2\" /></li></ul></div>\n\n<div class=\"section-lg\">\n\t<div class=\"container-fluid container-lg\">\n\t\t<p class=\"txt-18 txt-mincho txt-center-pc\">\n\t\t\tどのようなときも社員が働きやすい環境を整えることが、会社の使命であると考えます。<br>\n\t\t\tミズホでは、オフィスや工場などの環境整備からモチベーション維持、向上の制度まで、<br class=\"hidden-xs\">\n\t\t\t社員がイキイキと働ける環境づくりを目指しています。\n\t\t</p>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block-environment block-environment-01\">\n\t<div class=\"container-fluid container-lg\">\n\t\t<div class=\"row\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"col col-sm-6\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"inner-col\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"ttl mb-30\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"icon\"><img src=\"https://www.mizuho.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/mizuho1.2.7/img/common/icon-environment-01.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-responsive center-block\"></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"txt\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t事業拡大に伴う<br>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tオフィス環境の整備\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"txt-16\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t2013年には本社第2ビル、2018年には本社第3ビルを構え、千葉工場も習志野から佐倉へと移転・拡大をしています。計画的に社員が伸び伸びと働ける環境を整えています。\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n\t<div class=\"bg photo-ofi\">\n\t\t<img src=\"https://www.mizuho.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/mizuho1.2.7/img/common/img-environment-01.jpg\" alt=\"事業拡大に伴うオフィス環境の整備\">\n\t</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block-environment block-environment-02\">\n\t<div class=\"container-fluid container-lg\">\n\t\t<div class=\"row\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"col col-sm-6 col-sm-offset-6\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"inner-col\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"ttl mb-30\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"icon\"><img src=\"https://www.mizuho.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/mizuho1.2.7/img/common/icon-environment-02.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-responsive center-block\"></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"txt\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t事業拡大に伴う<br>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tオフィス環境の整備\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"txt-16\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tミズホの社是は「誠実」「奉仕」「団結」の３つです。<br>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t医療機器メーカーということもあり、この言葉が表すようにとても誠実で真面目な会社です。それは、働き方も仲間に対しても同じです。その証拠に当社には長期勤続者がとても多く、居心地のよい環境になっています。\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n\t<div class=\"bg photo-ofi\">\n\t\t<img src=\"https://www.mizuho.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/mizuho1.2.7/img/common/img-environment-02.jpg\" alt=\"居心地がよく、長期勤務者の多い誠実な社風\">\n\t</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block-environment block-environment-03 mb-30\">\n\t<div class=\"container-fluid container-lg\">\n\t\t<div class=\"row\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"col col-sm-6\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"inner-col\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"ttl mb-30\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"icon\"><img src=\"https://www.mizuho.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/mizuho1.2.7/img/common/icon-environment-03.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-responsive center-block\"></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"txt\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t常に向上心をもって<br>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t働ける教育・評価制度\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"txt-16\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t会社の成績・個人の成績に応じて評価される賞与や、学びたいと希望する社員へのサポート体制、また社員の将来を見据えた福利厚生など、モチベーションを維持し常に向上心を持って取り組める環境づくりにも力を入れています。\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n\t<div class=\"bg photo-ofi\">\n\t\t<img src=\"https://www.mizuho.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/mizuho1.2.7/img/common/img-environment-03.jpg\" alt=\"常に向上心をもって働ける教育・評価制度\">\n\t</div>\n</div>\n\n</main>\n\t<section class=\"section-requirements section-lg\">\n\t\t<div class=\"container-lg container-fluid\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"txt-center txt-main mb-40\">\n\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"txt-40 txt-eng ls-md mb-10\">Requirements</h2>\n\t\t\t\t<p class=\"txt-18 txt-mincho txt-bold ls-md lh-1\">募集要項</p>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"row row-min\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-xs-6\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://www.mizuho.co.jp/recruit/requirements-01/\" class=\"btn-requirements\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"inner\">新卒募集要項</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-xs-6\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://www.mizuho.co.jp/recruit/requirements-02/\" class=\"btn-requirements\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"inner\">中途募集要項</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</section>\n\n<foo